annotationA: Protein kinase, cGMP-dependent at 21D is a Mg[+] dependent-kinase that is activated by cGMP. It contributes to somatic muscle development, salivary gland morphogenesis and epithelial fluid transport
annotationB: 6-pyruvoyl tetrahydrobiopterin synthase; Required for pigment and biopterin synthesis; Belongs to the PTPS family
